General.Name: Winchester Energy Ltd
General.Description: Winchester Energy Limited, together with its subsidiaries, engages in the acquisition and exploration of oil and gas properties in the United States and Australia. It had approximately 17,622 net acres located in the Eastern Shelf of the Permian Basin in Texas. Winchester Energy Limited was incorporated in 2014 and is based in West Perth, Australia.
